Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:31.14,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}この瞬間、この場所がスタート
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.78,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}イメージしてみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.54,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}何ができるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:41.32,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}信じられない出来事だってある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:46.44,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}もっと… 越えていけるね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.57,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}power of dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.81,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}0から生まれるすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:57.29,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}輝いて fly あの空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.09,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}light blue wind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.26,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思いきり、羽ばたきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:08.67,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}最高のスマイルで 笑いながら さぁ、ゆこう!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:13.75,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}未知の世界へと今 飛び出そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:20.07,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}未来を選び、決めるのは自分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.47,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}夢を追いかけてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.03,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}泣く日もある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:29.68,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}それは大事な願い、消えないで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:34.55,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}きっと逢えるから 明日の君へ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:41.80,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}get out of the gate true sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:23.99,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}get out of the gate true sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:31.14,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}此刻從此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.78,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}試著想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.54,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}自己能做到什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:41.32,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}有出乎意料的變故
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:46.44,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能夠越過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.57,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}power of dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.81,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一切從0開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:57.29,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}閃耀著飛向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.09,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}light blue wind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.26,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}下定決心展翅飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:08.67,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}用最美的笑容  出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:13.75,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}現在向未知的世界起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:20.07,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}未來的選擇  做決定的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.47,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}去追逐夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.03,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}也會有想哭的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:29.68,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那是最重要的願望  不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:34.55,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能和明天的你再次相見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:41.80,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}get out of the gate true sky
